{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"We are here today"},{"time":2000,"text":"because [the] United Nations"},{"time":4000,"text":"have defined goals"},{"time":6000,"text":"for the progress of countries."},{"time":8000,"text":"They're called Millennium Development Goals."},{"time":11000,"text":"And the reason I really like these goals"},{"time":14000,"text":"is that there are eight of them."},{"time":17000,"text":"And by specifying eight different goals,"},{"time":19000,"text":"the United Nations has said"},{"time":21000,"text":"that there are so many things needed"},{"time":23000,"text":"to change in a country"},{"time":25000,"text":"in order to get the good life for people."},{"time":27000,"text":"Look here -- you have to end poverty,"},{"time":29000,"text":"education, gender,"},{"time":31000,"text":"child and maternal health,"},{"time":33000,"text":"control infections, protect the environment"},{"time":36000,"text":"and get the good global links between nations"},{"time":38000,"text":"in every aspect"},{"time":40000,"text":"from aid to trade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"There's a second reason I like these development goals,"},{"time":46000,"text":"and that is because each and every one is measured."},{"time":49000,"text":"Take child mortality;"},{"time":52000,"text":"the aim here is to reduce child mortality"},{"time":54000,"text":"by two-thirds,"},{"time":56000,"text":"from 1990 to 2015."},{"time":59000,"text":"That's a four percent reduction per year --"},{"time":63000,"text":"and this, with measuring."},{"time":65000,"text":"That's what makes the difference"},{"time":67000,"text":"between political talking like this"},{"time":69000,"text":"and really going for the important thing,"},{"time":71000,"text":"a better life for people."},{"time":74000,"text":"And what I'm so happy about with this"},{"time":76000,"text":"is that we have already documented"},{"time":78000,"text":"that there are many countries"},{"time":80000,"text":"in Asia, in the Middle East,"},{"time":82000,"text":"in Latin America and East Europe"},{"time":85000,"text":"that [are] reducing with this rate."},{"time":87000,"text":"And even mighty Brazil is going down with five percent per year,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and Turkey with seven percent per year."},{"time":92000,"text":"So there's good news."},{"time":94000,"text":"But then I hear people saying, \"There is no progress in Africa."},{"time":97000,"text":"And there's not even statistics on Africa"},{"time":99000,"text":"to know what is happening.\""},{"time":101000,"text":"I'll prove them wrong on both points."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"Come with me to the wonderful world of statistics."},{"time":107000,"text":"I bring you to the webpage, ChildMortality.org,"},{"time":110000,"text":"where you can take deaths in children"},{"time":112000,"text":"below five years of age for all countries --"},{"time":115000,"text":"it's done by U.N. specialists."},{"time":117000,"text":"And I will take Kenya as an example."},{"time":119000,"text":"Here you see the data."},{"time":121000,"text":"Don't panic -- don't panic now, I'll help you through this."},{"time":124000,"text":"It looks nasty, like in college"},{"time":126000,"text":"when you didn't like statistics."},{"time":128000,"text":"But first thing, when you see dots like this,"},{"time":130000,"text":"you have to ask yourself:"},{"time":132000,"text":"from where do the data come?"},{"time":134000,"text":"What is the origin of the data?"},{"time":136000,"text":"Is it so that in Kenya,"},{"time":138000,"text":"there are doctors and other specialists"},{"time":140000,"text":"who write the death certificate at the death of the child"},{"time":142000,"text":"and it's sent to the statistical office?"},{"time":144000,"text":"No -- low-income countries like Kenya"},{"time":147000,"text":"still don't have that level of organization."},{"time":150000,"text":"It exists, but it's not complete"},{"time":152000,"text":"because so many deaths occur in the home"},{"time":155000,"text":"with the family,"},{"time":157000,"text":"and it's not registered."},{"time":159000,"text":"What we rely on is not an incomplete system."},{"time":161000,"text":"We have interviews, we have surveys."},{"time":164000,"text":"And this is highly professional"},{"time":166000,"text":"female interviewers"},{"time":168000,"text":"who sit down for one hour with a woman"},{"time":170000,"text":"and ask her about [her] birth history."},{"time":172000,"text":"How many children did you have?"},{"time":174000,"text":"Are they alive?"},{"time":176000,"text":"If they died, at what age and what year?"},{"time":179000,"text":"And then this is done in a representative sample"},{"time":181000,"text":"of thousands of women in the country"},{"time":184000,"text":"and put together in what used to be called"},{"time":186000,"text":"a demographic health survey report."},{"time":189000,"text":"But these surveys are costly,"},{"time":191000,"text":"so they can only be done [in] three- to five-year intervals."},{"time":194000,"text":"But they have good quality."},{"time":196000,"text":"So this is a limitation."},{"time":198000,"text":"And all these colored lines here are results;"},{"time":201000,"text":"each color is one survey."},{"time":203000,"text":"But that's too complicated for today, so I'll simplify it for you,"},{"time":206000,"text":"and I give you one average point for each survey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"This was 1977, 1988,"},{"time":212000,"text":"1992, '97"},{"time":214000,"text":"and 2002."},{"time":217000,"text":"And when the experts in the U.N."},{"time":219000,"text":"have got these surveys in place in their database,"},{"time":222000,"text":"then they use advanced mathematical formulas"},{"time":225000,"text":"to produce a trend line, and the trend line looks like this."},{"time":228000,"text":"See here -- it's the best fit they can get of this point."},{"time":231000,"text":"But watch out --"},{"time":233000,"text":"they continue the line"},{"time":235000,"text":"beyond the last point"},{"time":237000,"text":"out into nothing."},{"time":239000,"text":"And they estimated that in 2008,"},{"time":242000,"text":"Kenya had per child mortality of 128."},{"time":245000,"text":"And I was sad,"},{"time":247000,"text":"because we could see"},{"time":249000,"text":"this reversal in Kenya"},{"time":251000,"text":"with an increased child mortality in the 90s."},{"time":254000,"text":"It was so tragic."},{"time":256000,"text":"But in June, I got a mail in my inbox"},{"time":259000,"text":"from Demographic Health Surveys,"},{"time":261000,"text":"and it showed good news from Kenya."},{"time":263000,"text":"I was so happy."},{"time":265000,"text":"This was the estimate of the new survey."},{"time":268000,"text":"Then it just took another three months"},{"time":270000,"text":"for [the] U.N. to get it into their server,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and on Friday we got the new trend line --"},{"time":275000,"text":"it was down here."},{"time":277000,"text":"Isn't it nice -- isn't it nice, yeah?"},{"time":279000,"text":"I was actually, on Friday, sitting in front of my computer,"},{"time":282000,"text":"and I saw the death rate fall"},{"time":284000,"text":"from 128 to 84 just that morning."},{"time":287000,"text":"So we celebrated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289000,"text":"But now, when you have this trend line,"},{"time":291000,"text":"how do we measure progress?"},{"time":293000,"text":"I'm going into some details here,"},{"time":295000,"text":"because [the] U.N. do it like this."},{"time":297000,"text":"They start [in] 1990 -- they measure to 2009."},{"time":300000,"text":"They say, \"0.9 percent, no progress.\""},{"time":303000,"text":"That's unfair."},{"time":305000,"text":"As a professor, I think I have the right to propose something differently."},{"time":308000,"text":"I would say, at least do this --"},{"time":310000,"text":"10 years is enough to follow the trend."},{"time":312000,"text":"It's two surveys, and you can see what's happening now."},{"time":315000,"text":"They have 2.4 percent."},{"time":317000,"text":"Had I been in the Ministry of Health in Kenya,"},{"time":319000,"text":"I may have joined these two points."},{"time":322000,"text":"So what I'm telling you"},{"time":324000,"text":"is that we know the child mortality."},{"time":326000,"text":"We have a decent trend."},{"time":328000,"text":"It's coming into some tricky things then"},{"time":330000,"text":"when we are measuring MDGs."},{"time":332000,"text":"And the reason here for Africa is especially important,"},{"time":335000,"text":"because '90s was a bad decade,"},{"time":337000,"text":"not only in Kenya, but across Africa."},{"time":340000,"text":"The HIV epidemic peaked."},{"time":342000,"text":"There was resistance for the old malaria drugs, until we got the new drugs."},{"time":345000,"text":"We got, later, the mosquito netting."},{"time":347000,"text":"And there was socio-economic problems,"},{"time":349000,"text":"which are now being solved at a much better scale."},{"time":352000,"text":"So look at the average here --"},{"time":354000,"text":"this is the average for all of sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":356000,"text":"And [the] U.N. says"},{"time":358000,"text":"it's a reduction with 1.8 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"Now this sounds a little theoretical,"},{"time":363000,"text":"but it's not so theoretical."},{"time":365000,"text":"You know, these economists,"},{"time":367000,"text":"they love money, they want more and more of it, they want it to grow."},{"time":370000,"text":"So they calculate the percent annual growth rate of [the] economy."},{"time":373000,"text":"We in public health, we hate child death,"},{"time":376000,"text":"so we want less and less and less of child deaths."},{"time":378000,"text":"So we calculate the percent reduction per year,"},{"time":380000,"text":"but it's sort of the same percentage."},{"time":382000,"text":"If your economy grows with four percent,"},{"time":384000,"text":"you ought to reduce child mortality four percent;"},{"time":386000,"text":"if it's used well and people are really involved"},{"time":389000,"text":"and can get the use of the resources in the way they want it."},{"time":392000,"text":"So is this fair now to measure this over 19 years?"},{"time":395000,"text":"An economist would never do that."},{"time":398000,"text":"I have just divided it into two periods."},{"time":400000,"text":"In the 90s, only 1.2 percent,"},{"time":403000,"text":"only 1.2 percent."},{"time":405000,"text":"Whereas now, second gear --"},{"time":407000,"text":"it's like Africa had first gear,"},{"time":409000,"text":"now they go into second gear."},{"time":411000,"text":"But even this"},{"time":413000,"text":"is not a fair representation of Africa,"},{"time":415000,"text":"because it's an average,"},{"time":417000,"text":"it's an average speed of reduction in Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419000,"text":"And look here when I take you into my bubble graphs."},{"time":422000,"text":"Still here,"},{"time":424000,"text":"child death per 1,000 on that axis."},{"time":427000,"text":"Here we have [the] year."},{"time":429000,"text":"And I'm now giving you a wider picture than the MDG."},{"time":432000,"text":"I start 50 years ago"},{"time":434000,"text":"when Africa celebrated independence in most countries."},{"time":437000,"text":"I give you Congo, which was high,"},{"time":439000,"text":"Ghana -- lower. And Kenya -- even lower."},{"time":441000,"text":"And what has happened over the years since then? Here we go."},{"time":444000,"text":"You can see, with independence, literacy improved"},{"time":447000,"text":"and vaccinations started, smallpox was eradicated,"},{"time":450000,"text":"hygiene was improved, and things got better."},{"time":453000,"text":"But then, in the '80s, watch out here."},{"time":455000,"text":"Congo got into civil war,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and they leveled off here."},{"time":459000,"text":"Ghana got very ahead, fast."},{"time":461000,"text":"This was the backlash in Kenya, and Ghana bypassed,"},{"time":464000,"text":"but then Kenya and Ghana go down together --"},{"time":466000,"text":"still a standstill in Congo."},{"time":468000,"text":"That's where we are today."},{"time":470000,"text":"You can see it doesn't make sense"},{"time":473000,"text":"to make an average of this zero improvement"},{"time":476000,"text":"and this very fast improvement."},{"time":480000,"text":"Time has come"},{"time":482000,"text":"to stop thinking about sub-Saharan Africa as one place."},{"time":486000,"text":"Their countries are so different,"},{"time":489000,"text":"and they merit to be recognized in the same way,"},{"time":492000,"text":"as we don't talk about Europe as one place."},{"time":494000,"text":"I can tell you that the economy in Greece and Sweden are very different --"},{"time":497000,"text":"everyone knows that."},{"time":499000,"text":"And they are judged, each country, on how they are doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"So let me show the wider picture."},{"time":505000,"text":"My country, Sweden:"},{"time":508000,"text":"1800, we were up there."},{"time":511000,"text":"What a strange personality disorder we must have,"},{"time":514000,"text":"counting the children so meticulously in spite of a high child death rate."},{"time":517000,"text":"It's very strange. It's sort of embarrassing."},{"time":520000,"text":"But we had that habit in Sweden, you know,"},{"time":522000,"text":"that we counted all the child deaths,"},{"time":524000,"text":"even if we didn't do anything about it."},{"time":526000,"text":"And then, you see, these were famine years."},{"time":528000,"text":"These were bad years, and people got fed up with Sweden."},{"time":530000,"text":"My ancestors moved to the United States."},{"time":533000,"text":"And eventually, soon they started to get better and better here."},{"time":536000,"text":"And here we got better education, and we got health service,"},{"time":539000,"text":"and child mortality came down."},{"time":541000,"text":"We never had a war; Sweden was in peace all this time."},{"time":544000,"text":"But look, the rate of lowering"},{"time":546000,"text":"in Sweden"},{"time":548000,"text":"was not fast."},{"time":550000,"text":"Sweden achieved a low child mortality"},{"time":553000,"text":"because we started early."},{"time":556000,"text":"We had primary school actually"},{"time":558000,"text":"started in 1842."},{"time":560000,"text":"And then you get that wonderful effect"},{"time":562000,"text":"when we got female literacy"},{"time":564000,"text":"one generation later."},{"time":566000,"text":"You have to realize that the investments we do in progress"},{"time":569000,"text":"are long-term investments."},{"time":571000,"text":"It's not about just five years --"},{"time":573000,"text":"it's long-term investments."},{"time":575000,"text":"And Sweden never reached [the] Millennium Development Goal rate,"},{"time":578000,"text":"3.1 percent when I calculated."},{"time":580000,"text":"So we are off track -- that's what Sweden is."},{"time":583000,"text":"But you don't talk about it so much."},{"time":585000,"text":"We want others to be better than we were, and indeed, others have been better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588000,"text":"Let me show you Thailand,"},{"time":590000,"text":"see what a success story, Thailand from the 1960s --"},{"time":592000,"text":"how they went down here"},{"time":594000,"text":"and reached almost the same child mortality levels as Sweden."},{"time":597000,"text":"And I'll give you another story -- Egypt,"},{"time":600000,"text":"the most hidden, glorious success in public health."},{"time":603000,"text":"Egypt was up here in 1960,"},{"time":605000,"text":"higher than Congo."},{"time":607000,"text":"The Nile Delta was a misery for children"},{"time":610000,"text":"with diarrheal disease"},{"time":612000,"text":"and malaria and a lot of problems."},{"time":614000,"text":"And then they got the Aswan Dam. They got electricity in their homes,"},{"time":617000,"text":"they increased education"},{"time":619000,"text":"and they got primary health care."},{"time":621000,"text":"And down they went, you know."},{"time":623000,"text":"And they got safer water, they eradicated malaria."},{"time":626000,"text":"And isn't it a success story."},{"time":628000,"text":"Millennium Development Goal rates for child mortality"},{"time":631000,"text":"is fully possible."},{"time":633000,"text":"And the good thing is"},{"time":635000,"text":"that Ghana today is going with the same rate"},{"time":637000,"text":"as Egypt did at its fastest."},{"time":640000,"text":"Kenya is now speeding up."},{"time":642000,"text":"Here we have a problem."},{"time":644000,"text":"We have a severe problem in countries which are at a standstill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"Now, let me now bring you to a wider picture,"},{"time":651000,"text":"a wider picture of child mortality."},{"time":653000,"text":"I'm going to show you the relationship"},{"time":655000,"text":"between child mortality on this axis here --"},{"time":658000,"text":"this axis here is child mortality --"},{"time":661000,"text":"and here I have the family size."},{"time":664000,"text":"The relationship between child mortality and family size."},{"time":666000,"text":"One, two, three, four children per woman:"},{"time":668000,"text":"six, seven, eight children per woman."},{"time":670000,"text":"This is, once again, 1960 --"},{"time":672000,"text":"50 years ago."},{"time":674000,"text":"Each bubble is a country --"},{"time":676000,"text":"the color, you can see, a continent."},{"time":678000,"text":"The dark blue here is sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":680000,"text":"And the size of the bubble is the population."},{"time":684000,"text":"And these are"},{"time":686000,"text":"the so-called \"developing\" countries."},{"time":688000,"text":"They had high, or very high, child mortality"},{"time":691000,"text":"and family size, six to eight."},{"time":694000,"text":"And the ones over there,"},{"time":696000,"text":"they were so-called Western countries."},{"time":698000,"text":"They had low child mortality"},{"time":700000,"text":"and small families."},{"time":702000,"text":"What has happened?"},{"time":704000,"text":"What I want you [to do] now is to see with your own eyes"},{"time":707000,"text":"the relation between fall in child mortality"},{"time":710000,"text":"and decrease in family size."},{"time":713000,"text":"I just want not to have any room for doubt --"},{"time":715000,"text":"you have to see that for yourself."},{"time":717000,"text":"This is what happened. Now I start the world."},{"time":720000,"text":"Here we come down with the eradication of"},{"time":722000,"text":"smallpox, better education,"},{"time":724000,"text":"health service."},{"time":726000,"text":"It got down there -- China comes into the Western box here."},{"time":729000,"text":"And here Brazil is in the Western Box."},{"time":731000,"text":"India is approaching. The first African countries coming into the Western box,"},{"time":734000,"text":"and we get a lot a new neighbors."},{"time":736000,"text":"Welcome to a decent life."},{"time":738000,"text":"Come on. We want everyone down there."},{"time":740000,"text":"This is the vision we have, isn't it."},{"time":742000,"text":"And look now, the first African countries here are coming in."},{"time":745000,"text":"There we are today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748000,"text":"There is no such thing"},{"time":750000,"text":"as a \"Western world\" and \"developing world.\""},{"time":752000,"text":"This is the report from [the] U.N.,"},{"time":754000,"text":"which came out on Friday."},{"time":756000,"text":"It's very good -- \"Levels and Trends in Child Mortality\" --"},{"time":759000,"text":"except this page."},{"time":761000,"text":"This page is very bad;"},{"time":763000,"text":"it's a categorization of countries."},{"time":766000,"text":"It labels \"developing countries,\" -- I can read from the list here --"},{"time":769000,"text":"developing countries: Republic of Korea -- South Korea."},{"time":772000,"text":"Huh?"},{"time":774000,"text":"They get Samsung, how can they be [a] developing country?"},{"time":777000,"text":"They have here Singapore."},{"time":779000,"text":"They have the lowest child mortality in the world, Singapore."},{"time":781000,"text":"They bypassed Sweden five years ago,"},{"time":783000,"text":"and they are labeled a developing country."},{"time":785000,"text":"They have here Qatar."},{"time":787000,"text":"It's the richest country in the world with Al Jazeera."},{"time":789000,"text":"How the heck could they be [a] developing country?"},{"time":791000,"text":"This is crap."},{"time":793000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":796000,"text":"The rest here is good -- the rest is good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":798000,"text":"We have to have a modern concept,"},{"time":800000,"text":"which fits to the data."},{"time":802000,"text":"And we have to realize"},{"time":804000,"text":"that we are all going to into this, down to here."},{"time":807000,"text":"What is the importance now with the relations here."},{"time":810000,"text":"Look -- even if we look in Africa --"},{"time":812000,"text":"these are the African countries."},{"time":814000,"text":"You can clearly see the relation with falling child mortality"},{"time":817000,"text":"and decreasing family size,"},{"time":819000,"text":"even within Africa."},{"time":821000,"text":"It's very clear that this is what happens."},{"time":823000,"text":"And a very important piece of research came out on Friday"},{"time":826000,"text":"from the Institute of Health Metrics and Evaluation in Seattle"},{"time":830000,"text":"showing that almost 50 percent"},{"time":832000,"text":"of the fall in child mortality"},{"time":834000,"text":"can be attributed to female education."},{"time":837000,"text":"That is, when we get girls in school,"},{"time":840000,"text":"we'll get an impact 15 to 20 years later,"},{"time":842000,"text":"which is a secular trend which is very strong."},{"time":845000,"text":"That's why we must have that long-term perspective,"},{"time":848000,"text":"but we must measure the impact"},{"time":850000,"text":"over 10-year periods."},{"time":852000,"text":"It's fully possible"},{"time":854000,"text":"to get child mortality down in all of these countries"},{"time":856000,"text":"and to get them down in the corner"},{"time":858000,"text":"where we all would like to live together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":862000,"text":"And of course, lowering child mortality"},{"time":865000,"text":"is a matter of utmost importance"},{"time":868000,"text":"from humanitarian aspects."},{"time":870000,"text":"It's a decent life for children,"},{"time":872000,"text":"we are talking about."},{"time":874000,"text":"But it is also a strategic investment"},{"time":877000,"text":"in the future of all mankind,"},{"time":879000,"text":"because it's about the environment."},{"time":882000,"text":"We will not be able to manage the environment"},{"time":884000,"text":"and avoid the terrible climate crisis"},{"time":886000,"text":"if we don't stabilize the world population."},{"time":888000,"text":"Let's be clear about that."},{"time":890000,"text":"And the way to do that,"},{"time":892000,"text":"that is to get child mortality down, get access to family planning"},{"time":895000,"text":"and behind that drive female education."},{"time":898000,"text":"And that is fully possible. Let's do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":902000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}